{"tid":361268,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果當初孟達投吳","createTime":"2017-08-16T03:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T03:01:25.000Z","uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c1586511f31cb49d7fb3eac9ed1bb550ae44cc","tid":361268,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"咁仲達係唔係擒斬吳孟達<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30540f3534f1277df207c084c5ee795345e7895","tid":361268,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad15cd1b8f96d3e8722d404ffaf6f2b4d9052e02","tid":361268,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/5668.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F5668.jpg&h=4190bb90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad3c262b00f0c22a1dbaef1f11b034f1e32fd9ff","tid":361268,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af06496f1948b549b26dc4830e4871ccceebed1","tid":361268,"uid":36029,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"《富比世》（Forbes）雜誌歸納出5點運用幽默感的正確技巧：<br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n（１）別忘記自己的身分，如果身為主管，領導或管理才是你最重要的工作任務，而不是扮演一個喜劇演員。<br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n（２）作為朋友，彼此開玩笑吐槽或許無傷大雅；但主管跟員工開玩笑吐槽可就一點也不幽默，除非彼此之間長時間的工作情誼或穩固的信任感。<br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n（３）開自己玩笑不一定是幽默的表現，很可能因此傷人而不自知。特別是領導者，你的發言代表的並非個人，而是團隊，因此當你開自己玩笑時，很可能傷害了團隊。<br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（４）如果自己個性實在不適合，就別勉強自己耍幽默，以免弄巧成拙，氣氛冷場。</span><br />\n&nbsp; <br />\n（５）幽默感也要看對象，你的玩笑幽默與否決定權在對方，而不在於你。如果對方不覺得幽默，那麼你的一番好意倒成了惡意。"},{"pid":"e49a55f20f515f400d1816edc84d764b9ed8a2fe","tid":361268,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幽默感呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我平時唔係咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168568c6458635801cb54041f9bd351dbc8bed32","tid":361268,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f908dc209f3a5f64dc3f187e90618665befb9c7","tid":361268,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}